snippet.title: Lego Rock Band Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description: So here's the trailer launched in public to attract as much as people as possible... Blah... I don't think game will go good... If people want Lego game they'll buy Batman or Indiana Jones, if they want music game they'll get Rock Band or Guitar Hero...
